cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.DB 

This paper discusses the use of ontology and ontology learning, which are common topics in the sub-categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), information retrieval (cs.IR), and machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper evaluates different methods for taxonomic relation extraction, which is a common topic in the sub-category of databases (cs.DB).
